OL,3,CLabour could lose more than 50 seats
OL,4,Cin Birmingham, poll suggests
OL,6,FA new poll on the eve of the local
OL,7,Felections suggests Labour could see
OL,8,Fits biggest ever loss in Birmingham.
OL,10,FThe poll by research group More in
OL,11,FCommon shows Labour candidates almost
OL,12,Fwiped out and Reform UK surging to 47
OL,13,Fseats.
OL,15,FIt is an even more devastating
OL,16,Fprediction than the ITV News Central
OL,17,Fpoll with More in Common published in
OL,18,FApril.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
