OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778227271
OL,3,CLabour could lose more than 50 seats
OL,4,Cin Birmingham, poll suggests
OL,6,FAnother big winner from this poll is
OL,7,Fthat Independents would become the
OL,8,Fsecond-largest group in Birmingham
OL,9,FCity Council.
OL,11,FThis makes for pretty bleak reading
OL,12,Ffor Labour councillors in the second
OL,13,Fcity and across the country.
OL,15,FIf it came true, this disaster would
OL,16,Foutstrip Labour's biggest ever defeat
OL,17,Fin the council by 22 seats.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
