CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778227271
OL,3,CLabour could lose more than 50 seats
OL,4,Cin Birmingham, poll suggests
OL,6,FThe poll predicts Reform UK to get 47
OL,7,Fseats, Independents to get 17, Labour
OL,8,Fto have 14, The Greens 12,
OL,9,FConservatives 6 and Lib Dems 5.
OL,11,FWith every party other than the Tories
OL,12,Fruling out working with Reform, it
OL,13,Fseems a right-wing coalition would be
OL,14,Fthe most likely outcome.
OL,16,FThe vote share is estimated as 26% for
OL,17,FReform UK, 23% for Labour, 18% for the
OL,18,FGreens, 15% for the Conservatives, 12%
OL,19,Ffor Independents and 7% for the
OL,20,FLibdems.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
