OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778227271
OL,3,CLabour could lose more than 50 seats
OL,4,Cin Birmingham, poll suggests
OL,6,FThis result is radical and should be
OL,7,Ftaken with a pinch of salt. More in
OL,8,FCommon says this shift in popularity
OL,9,Ffor Reform UK has been led by older
OL,10,Fvoters but is till within their margin.
OL,12,FPolling on local elections has a
OL,13,Flarger margin of error than national
OL,14,Fpolling, especially when predicting
OL,15,Fseat numbers.
OL,17,FBut the sample size is huge at 1,794,
OL,18,Fand all the people asked said they
OL,19,Fwould definitely vote.
OL,21,FHow big is this?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
