OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778227271
OL,3,CLabour could lose more than 50 seats
OL,4,Cin Birmingham, poll suggests
OL,6,FWhile it is true that the only poll
OL,7,Fthat matters is the vote on 7 May, if
OL,8,Fthis result is replicated in ballots
OL,9,Fcast on Thursday, it will be explosive
OL,10,Fnot only for Labour in Birmingham but
OL,11,Falso for the Prime Minister and even
OL,12,Fthe idea of a Labour Party and
OL,13,FConservative Party.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/8
